  "title": "Freelance Debt Consultant",
  "description": "<h1><strong>About us</strong></h1><h2><strong>Who We Are</strong></h2><p>Debt Assist is a trusted Singapore-based Debt Consultancy agency specializing in providing expert guidance and tailored solutions to help clients conquer their consumer debt and regain control of their financial future.</p><h2><strong>Our Mission</strong></h2><p>To offer personalized strategies that suit clients’ unique financial circumstances and goals.</p><h2><strong>Job Opening</strong></h2><p>We are recruiting freelance Debt Consultants to join our team. </p><p>The ideal candidate will be individuals who are enthusiastic about helping people, possess strong communication skills, and enjoy interacting with others.</p><h2><strong>What you'll be doing</strong></h2><p>The Debt Consultant will mainly be responsible for providing tailored debt management solutions to clients. Day-to-day tasks include: </p><p>Listening to clients’ to understand their unique financial circumstances</p><p>Analyzing clients' financial situations, </p><p>Offering personalized advice and tailored solutions to clients, </p><p>Whilst always maintaining clear and professional communication.</p><h2><strong>What we're looking for</strong></h2><p>No background in finance or consultancy is required. </p><p>We provide basic training to bring you up to task.</p><p>- Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p><h2><strong>What we offer</strong></h2><p>Attractive Commission and earning potential\t</p><p>Flexible Work Arrangements</p>",
